qolibri2
========

This is a fork of the original qolibiri EPWING dictionary viewer, the
development of which halted at version 1.0.4 back in 2008 [1]. This fork
will get version numbers >= 1.9.

Milestones for the 2.0 release
==============================

    * Fix GUI translations (1.9)
    * Port the GUI from being constructed manually to being editable
      with qt-designer (1.10)
    * Make the GUI capable of being driven keyboard-only (1.11)
    * Enable full regex search (1.12)
    * Fix font selection capabilitiy (dedicated Western and Japanese
      fonts) (1.13)
    * Regex-based custom substitution and highlighting (1.14)
    * Re-implement the search API as a web-based frontend to a qolibri
      server: qt-webkit for the GUI (1.15)
    * Write a ncurses client for the new qolibri server (1.16)
    * Port from Qt4 to Qt5 (1.17)

For TODOs, see the TODO file.

